nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE HOLDING STEADY AS IT MOVES NORTHWESTWARD...
summary: ...HENRIETTE HOLDING STEADY AS IT MOVES NORTHWESTWARD... As of 5:00 PM HST Sun Aug 10 the center of Henriette was located near 26.8, -153.8 with movement NW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 990 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 80 mph.
